[{"Id": 1016640, "EnglishTitle": "PLEASE NOTE: Be it clear that the reason for presenting Translation is to understand Salaat and to recite in Arabic with concentration because reciting Salaat other than Arabic language (or Transliteration) is not correct.", "GujaratiTitle": null, "RUrduTitle": "Waazeh rahe keh tarjuma-e-namaz pesh karne ki asal wajah namaz samajh ke Arabi mein khuzoo aur tawajjoh ke saath namaz padhna hai. Kyu’n keh Arabi ya Roman-Arabi (Transliteration) ke siwa kisi aur zabaan mein namaz padhna sahih nahin hai.", "UrduTitle": "واضح رہے کہ ترجمۂ نماز پیش کرنے کی اصل غرض نماز سمجھ کے عربی میں خضوع اور توجہ کے ساتھ نماز پڑھنا ہے۔ کیوں کہ عربی کے سوا کسی اور زبان میں نماز پڑھنا صحیح نہیں ہے۔ اس لئے ہر ایک کے لئے نماز کی حد تک قرآن و عربی سیکھنا واجب ہے۔", "Sequence": null, "EnglishDescription": null, "GujaratiDescription": null, "RUrduDescription": null, "UrduDescription": null, "English": null, "Gujarati": null, "RGujarati": null, "RUrdu": null, "Urdu": null, "RArabic": null, "ArabicText1": null, "ArabicGreenSign1": null, "ArabicRedSign1": null, "ArabicBlueSign1": null, "ArabicText2": null, "ArabicGreenSign2": null, "ArabicRedSign2": null, "ArabicBlueSign2": null, "ArabicText3": null, "ArabicGreenSign3": null, "ArabicRedSign3": null, "ArabicBlueSign3": null, "ArabicText4": null, "ArabicGreenSign4": null, "ArabicRedSign4": null, "ArabicBlueSign4": null, "ArabicText5": null, "ArabicGreenSign5": null, "ArabicRedSign5": null, "ArabicBlueSign5": null, "ArabicText6": null, "ArabicGreenSign6": null, "ArabicRedSign6": null, "ArabicBlueSign6": null, "ArabicText7": null, "ArabicGreenSign7": null, "ArabicRedSign7": null, "ArabicBlueSign7": null, "ArabicText8": null, "ArabicGreenSign8": null, "ArabicRedSign8": null, "ArabicBlueSign8": null, "ArabicText9": null, "ArabicGreenSign9": null, "ArabicRedSign9": null, "ArabicBlueSign9": null, "ArabicText10": null, "ArabicGreenSign10": null, "ArabicRedSign10": null, "ArabicBlueSign10": null, "ArabicText11": null, "ArabicGreenSign11": null, "ArabicRedSign11": null, "ArabicBlueSign11": null, "ArabicText12": null, "ArabicGreenSign12": null, "ArabicRedSign12": null, "ArabicBlueSign12": null, "ArabicText13": null, "ArabicGreenSign13": null, "ArabicRedSign13": null, "ArabicBlueSign13": null, "ArabicText14": null, "ArabicGreenSign14": null, "ArabicRedSign14": null, "ArabicBlueSign14": null, "ArabicText15": null, "ArabicGreenSign15": null, "ArabicRedSign15": null, "ArabicBlueSign15": null, "ArabicText16": null, "ArabicGreenSign16": null, "ArabicRedSign16": null, "ArabicBlueSign16": null, "ArabicText17": null, "ArabicGreenSign17": null, "ArabicRedSign17": null, "ArabicBlueSign17": null, "ArabicText18": null, "ArabicGreenSign18": null, "ArabicRedSign18": null, "ArabicBlueSign18": null, "ArabicText19": null, "ArabicGreenSign19": null, "ArabicRedSign19": null, "ArabicBlueSign19": null, "ArabicText20": null, "ArabicGreenSign20": null, "ArabicRedSign20": null, "ArabicBlueSign20": null, "EnglishImage": null, "GujaratiImage": null, "RUrduImage": null, "UrduImage": null, "IsRed": 0, "MinimizeDescriptionLine": 0, "IsPrintable": 0}, {"Id": 1002827, "EnglishTitle": null, "GujaratiTitle": null, "RUrduTitle": null, "UrduTitle": null, "Sequence": null, "EnglishDescription": "As quoted from Makarim al-Akhlaq When you go to sleep at night, you may put close to the side of your head a clean vessel full of pure water and covered by a clean piece of cloth. When you wake up to offer the Night Prayer, you may drink three doses of that water and perform Wuzu with the rest of it. You may then turn your face towards the qiblah direction, recite the Azaan and Iqamah, and offer a 2 rakat namaz, reciting whatever Surah you would like to recite. While in ruku, repeat the following statement 25 times…", "GujaratiDescription": null, "RUrduDescription": "Makarimul Akhlaq mein hai keh raat mein sooney se pehle ek paak saaf bartan mein paani bhar ke apne paas rakkhe aur paak kapde se uska mooh baandh de, jab raat ke aakhri hisse mein Namaz-e-Shab ke liye uthay to us bartan se 3 ghoont paani peeye’n aur baaqi bache huwe paani se Wuzu kar le, phir qiblah rukh ho kar Azaan o Iqamah kahe aur 2 rakat namaz adaa kare jisme <Surah Fateha> ke baad koi bhi Surah padhe aur jab Ruku mein jaaye to 25 martaba kahe…", "UrduDescription": "مکارم الاخلاق میں ہے کہ جب تم رات کو سونے لگو تو ایک پاک صاف برتن میں پانی بھر کے اپنے پاس رکھو اور پاک کپڑے سے اس کا منہ باندھ دو جب رات کے آخری حصے میں نماز تہجد کے لئے اٹھو تو اس برتن سے تین گھونٹ پانی پیو اور بقیہ پانی سے وضو کر کے قبلہ رخ ہوکر اذان و اقامت کہو اور ۲ رکعت نماز ادا کرو ان ۲ رکعتوں میں <سورۂ فاتحہ> کے بعد جو سورہ چاہو پڑھو جب حمد اور سورہ پڑھ لو تو رکوع میں جا کر۲۵ مر تبہ کہو۔۔۔", "English": null, "Gujarati": null, "RGujarati": null, "RUrdu": null, "Urdu": null, "RArabic": null, "ArabicText1": null, "ArabicGreenSign1": null, "ArabicRedSign1": null, "ArabicBlueSign1": null, "ArabicText2": null, "ArabicGreenSign2": null, "ArabicRedSign2": null, "ArabicBlueSign2": null, "ArabicText3": null, "ArabicGreenSign3": null, "ArabicRedSign3": null, "ArabicBlueSign3": null, "ArabicText4": null, "ArabicGreenSign4": null, "ArabicRedSign4": null, "ArabicBlueSign4": null, "ArabicText5": null, "ArabicGreenSign5": null, "ArabicRedSign5": null, "ArabicBlueSign5": null, "ArabicText6": null, "ArabicGreenSign6": null, "ArabicRedSign6": null, "ArabicBlueSign6": null, "ArabicText7": null, "ArabicGreenSign7": null, "ArabicRedSign7": null, "ArabicBlueSign7": null, "ArabicText8": null, "ArabicGreenSign8": null, "ArabicRedSign8": null, "ArabicBlueSign8": null, "ArabicText9": null, "ArabicGreenSign9": null, "ArabicRedSign9": null, "ArabicBlueSign9": null, "ArabicText10": null, "ArabicGreenSign10": null, "ArabicRedSign10": null, "ArabicBlueSign10": null, "ArabicText11": null, "ArabicGreenSign11": null, "ArabicRedSign11": null, "ArabicBlueSign11": null, "ArabicText12": null, "ArabicGreenSign12": null, "ArabicRedSign12": null, "ArabicBlueSign12": null, "ArabicText13": null, "A