edSign7": null, "ArabicBlueSign7": null, "ArabicText8": null, "ArabicGreenSign8": null, "ArabicRedSign8": null, "ArabicBlueSign8": null, "ArabicText9": null, "ArabicGreenSign9": null, "ArabicRedSign9": null, "ArabicBlueSign9": null, "ArabicText10": null, "ArabicGreenSign10": null, "ArabicRedSign10": null, "ArabicBlueSign10": null, "ArabicText11": null, "ArabicGreenSign11": null, "ArabicRedSign11": null, "ArabicBlueSign11": null, "ArabicText12": null, "ArabicGreenSign12": null, "ArabicRedSign12": null, "ArabicBlueSign12": null, "ArabicText13": null, "ArabicGreenSign13": null, "ArabicRedSign13": null, "ArabicBlueSign13": null, "ArabicText14": null, "ArabicGreenSign14": null, "ArabicRedSign14": null, "ArabicBlueSign14": null, "ArabicText15": null, "ArabicGreenSign15": null, "ArabicRedSign15": null, "ArabicBlueSign15": null, "ArabicText16": null, "ArabicGreenSign16": null, "ArabicRedSign16": null, "ArabicBlueSign16": null, "ArabicText17": null, "ArabicGreenSign17": null, "ArabicRedSign17": null, "ArabicBlueSign17": null, "ArabicText18": null, "ArabicGreenSign18": null, "ArabicRedSign18": null, "ArabicBlueSign18": null, "ArabicText19": null, "ArabicGreenSign19": null, "ArabicRedSign19": null, "ArabicBlueSign19": null, "ArabicText20": null, "ArabicGreenSign20": null, "ArabicRedSign20": null, "ArabicBlueSign20": null, "EnglishImage": null, "GujaratiImage": null, "RUrduImage": null, "UrduImage": null, "IsRed": 0, "MinimizeDescriptionLine": 0, "IsPrintable": 0}, {"Id": 1002829, "EnglishTitle": null, "GujaratiTitle": null, "RUrduTitle": null, "UrduTitle": null, "Sequence": null, "EnglishDescription": "When you stand erect again after the ruku, you may repeat the same statement 25 times. In the two prostrations of the prayer and the position of sitting between them, you may repeat the same statement 25 each. When you stand up for offering the 2nd rakat, you may do the same thing as exactly as you have done in the 1st rakat. By this, you have repeated this statement 300 times. After namaz keeping yourself in the same position (ie. sitting), you may raise your head towards the sky and repeat the following statement 30 times…", "GujaratiDescription": null, "RUrduDescription": "Phir Ruku se seedha khade ho kar wohi jumla 25 martaba dauraaye aur is tarah 2 sajdoh mein, 2 sajdoh ke darminaay aur 2nd Sajdeh ke baad. Phir 2nd rakat ke liye khade ho aur usey bhi 1st rakat ki tarah anjaam de yaani 2 rakat namaz mein 300 martaba yeh jumle adaa honge. Namaz ke fauran baad bina koi harkat kiye huwe apne sar ko aasmaan ki taraf buland kar ke is zikr ko 30 martaba dauraaye…", "UrduDescription": "پھر رکوع سے سر اٹھا کر یہی ذکر ۲۵ مرتبہ کہواور سجدے میں جاکر بھی ۲۵ مرتبہ یہی کہو پھر دوسرے سجدے میں جاکر ۲۵ مرتبہ یہی کہو اور سجدے سے سر اٹھا کر ۲۵ مرتبہ یہی کہو اس کے بعد دوسری رکعت کے لئے کھڑے ہو جاؤ اور اسے بھی مذ کورہ طریقے سے پورا کرو اس طرح ذکر کی مجموعی تعداد ۳۰۰ ہوجاتی ہے پھر تشہد و سلام پڑھ کر نماز کو تمام کرو سلام کے بعد اپنا سر آسمان کی طرف بلند کر کے ۳۰ مرتبہ کہو۔۔۔", "English": null, "Gujarati": null, "RGujarati": null, "RUrdu": null, "Urdu": null, "RArabic": null, "ArabicText1": null, "ArabicGreenSign1": null, "ArabicRedSign1": null, "ArabicBlueSign1": null, "ArabicText2": null, "ArabicGreenSign2": null, "ArabicRedSign2": null, "ArabicBlueSign2": null, "ArabicText3": null, "ArabicGreenSign3": null, "ArabicRedSign3": null, "ArabicBlueSign3": null, "ArabicText4": null, "ArabicGreenSign4": null, "ArabicRedSign4": null, "ArabicBlueSign4": null, "ArabicText5": null, "ArabicGreenSign5": null, "ArabicRedSign5": null, "ArabicBlueSign5": null, "ArabicText6": null, "ArabicGreenSign6": null, "ArabicRedSign6": null, "ArabicBlueSign6": null, "ArabicText7": null, "ArabicGreenSign7": null, "ArabicRedSign7": null, "ArabicBlueSign7": null, "ArabicText8": null, "ArabicGreenSign8": null, "ArabicRedSign8": null, "ArabicBlueSign8": null, "ArabicText9": null, "ArabicGreenSign9": null, "ArabicRedSign9": null, "ArabicBlueSign9": null, "ArabicText10": null, "ArabicGreenS